whereas.text:
Whereas the United States recognizes the discovery of
			 significant offshore gas reserves in the Exclusive Economic Zone of the
			 Republic of Cyprus;

Whereas the United States supports the sovereign rights of
			 the Republic of Cyprus and Israel to explore and process energy reserves in
			 accordance with international law;

Whereas this discovery could potentially provide greater
			 energy security for Europe and Israel as well as act as a stabilizing and
			 unifying factor in the Eastern Mediterranean;
